---
// FAQ component for Destiny On Board – optimized using native <details> and Tailwind
---

<section class="py-16 bg-white" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 id="faq-heading" class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
        Frequently Asked Questions❓
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item -->
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden transition-all">
        <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          Do I have to pay for the consultation?
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-xl">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 pt-2 text-gray-600">
          Nope. Your first consultation is 100% free. We'll help you understand your options and give you a personalized migration plan—no strings attached.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden transition-all">
        <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          Is this a visa agency?
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-xl">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 pt-2 text-gray-600">
          No. We're not a typical agency. We're a team of people who've lived the same journey—and now help students plan it with clarity, step-by-step.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden transition-all">
        <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          Can you guarantee I'll get a visa or PR?
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-xl">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 pt-2 text-gray-600">
          We don't believe in fake promises. What we offer is strategy, clarity, and honest guidance to improve your chances based on your real situation.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden transition-all">
        <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          Who will I talk to during the consultation?
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-xl">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 pt-2 text-gray-600">
          You'll speak with someone from our team who understands your goals and situation. Not a robot. Not a generic advisor. A real person who's done this before.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden transition-all">
        <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          What's included in the free plan?
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-xl">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 pt-2 text-gray-600">
          <p>We'll map out:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-600">
            <li>Timelines, key requirements, and first steps</li>
            <li>Your best options based on your current visa or goal</li>
            <li>What programs make sense for your case</li>
            <li>A step-by-step strategy to stay or study</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
